snippet.title: Zowie EC2-B Review - Gaming Mouse
snippet.description:
In this video, I review the new Zowie EC2-B.

Zowie EC2-B: https://amzn.to/2FlXaA5
Zowie FK1 (Ambidextrous): https://amzn.to/2uq9Y3o

If you thought this Zowie Ec2-b review was helpful leave a like. It'd greatly help me out, as I'm just getting started on YouTube! 

So which kind of gaming mice are you a fan of? Do you like performance and practical or flashy and high-tech?

UPDATE: I've been using this mouse for about 8 months so far, and there seems to be no sign of wear on the feet, cable or button actuations. The shell has some very slight, finger marks on the left and right clicks. No wear on two side buttons on this zowie ec2-b.
